FBIS3-16739 "drsov054_m_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-054 Document Type:Daily Report 20 Mar 1994 Tajikistan Talks Held in Afghan Port on Return of Refugees LD2003132294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 0100 GMT 20 Mar 94 LD2003132294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network Language: Tajik Article Type:BFN [Text] Tahir Ahmadov, one of the leaders of the working group dealing with the return of the Tajik refugees from the Islamic State of Afghanistan held talks in Sherkhan Bander district, lower Pyanj, with Haji Farid Farukh, acting head of this port [Sherkhan Bander, in Afghanistan]. During the talks, questions related to the return of the Tajik refugees from Afghanistan and political problems in Afghanistan that are hindering the return of the refugees. Currently, more than 600 refugees have gathered in the port wanting to return home.
